#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:2 43329f61c23d46d28006d3ba0de6b815
msgid "储存"
msgstr "Storage"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:17 03d4a3f2e88846038bc9a5405631881a
msgid "ESP32 Flash 空间与使用要求？"
msgstr "What are the ESP32 Flash space and usage requirements?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:19 7eeb915b8a8e4ffc935db3914cf03060
msgid "外部 Flash 可以同时映射到 CPU 指令和只读数据空间。外部 Flash 最大可支持 16 MB。"
msgstr "External Flash can be mapped to both CPU instruction space and read-only data space. External Flash supports up to 16 MB."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:21 4484c12bf3fc4127909ad8f86b4888df
msgid "当映射到 CPU 指令空间时，一次最多可映射 11 MB + 248 KB。如果一次映射超过 3 MB + 248 KB， 则 Cache 性能可能由于 CPU 的推测性读取而降低。"
msgstr "When mapped to CPU instruction space, up to 11 MB + 248 KB can be mapped at a time. If more than 3 MB + 248 KB is mapped at a time, Cache performance may be reduced due to speculative reads by the CPU."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:22 7e85f2163d4541f284f05e3b92f29fcb
msgid "当映射到只读数据空间时，一次最多可以映射 4 MB。支持 8-bit、16-bit 和 32-bit 读取。"
msgstr "When mapped to read-only data space, up to 4 MB can be mapped at a time. 8-bit, 16-bit, and 32-bit reads are supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:27 a77f6d818ccb4219830c152415e23ba1
msgid "使用 ESP32 模组，如何查看模组的 PSRAM 的大小？"
msgstr "When using an ESP32 module, how can I check the PSRAM size of the module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:29 ba9ee9ddfc0540d5ac3022aa250a14e7
msgid "需要先在 make menuconfig 中配置开启 PSRAM 功能。PSRAM 的大小可通过 bootloader 的 log 信息或调用 esp_spiram_get_size() 来查看。"
msgstr "You need to enable the PSRAM function in make menuconfig first. The PSRAM size can be checked from the bootloader log information or by calling esp_spiram_get_size()."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:34 ddcb632b4048478b85af8ad1e8bc17e4
msgid "ESP32 外接 PSRAM 后，如何更改 PSRAM 的 clock 来源？"
msgstr "After connecting external PSRAM to ESP32, how can I change the clock source of PSRAM?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:36 dd6db32de3334abfa127d96ca03cc6b9
msgid "在 menuconfig 中修改。具体位置：menuconfig -> Component config -> ESP32-specific -> SPI RAM config。"
msgstr "Modify it in menuconfig. The specific path is: menuconfig -> Component config -> ESP32-specific -> SPI RAM config."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:41 ae1a713dda7d4e5bbb3178d6a025074d
msgid "ESP8266 是否可以搭配 TF 卡使用？"
msgstr "Can ESP8266 be used with a TF card?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:43 9403be3f4b9a416db792c2dd02172fab
msgid "不建议这么使用。"
msgstr "This usage is not recommended."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:45 878604c45fb24aa7b4f23ca887949b45
msgid "虽然硬件上是可以连接的（通过 spi 与 TF 卡通信），但是因为 ESP8266 的资源有限，根据不同的应用场景，很可能会出现内存不足等情况。所以不建议 ESP8266 搭配 TF 卡使用。"
msgstr "Although it can be connected in hardware (communicating with the TF card through SPI), ESP8266 has limited resources. Depending on the application scenario, insufficient memory and other issues may occur. Therefore, using ESP8266 with a TF card is not recommended."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:46 862a5701dc1746ed8bf9c47407570a1b
msgid "如果您只需要单 Wi-Fi 模组，并且要连接 TF 卡，建议使用 `ESP32-S2 <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32-s2_datasheet_cn.pdf>`_ 芯片。"
msgstr "If you only need a single Wi-Fi module and need to connect a TF card, it is recommended to use the `ESP32-S2 <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32-s2_datasheet_cn.pdf>`_ chip."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:51 40862b76afab4856bf3afa2108874f06
msgid "若每分钟保存或者更新数据到 flash 中，ESP32 设备的 NVS 能否满足该需求？"
msgstr "If data is saved or updated to Flash every minute, can the NVS of an ESP32 device meet this requirement?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:53 66cd32737d2a434fb8cad792c00124f6
msgid "根据 `NVS 说明 <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/storage/nvs_flash.html>`_，NVS 库在其操作中主要使用两个实体：页面和条目。逻辑页面对应 flash 的一个物理扇区。假设 flash 扇区大小为 4096 字节，每个页面可容纳 126 个条目(每个条目大小为 32 字节)，页面的其余部分用于页头部（32字节）和条目状态位图（32字节）。每个扇区的典型 flash 寿命为 100k 个擦除周期。假设期待设备的运行时间为 10 年，每分钟写入 flash 的数据大小为 4 字节，并且不使用 flash 加密：计算 flash 写操作的次数 60×24×365×10=5256000，在 NVS 中，会导致不超过 42k 个擦除周期(5256000/126)， 42k < 100k，因此，即使在没有多扇区影响的情况下也可以支持。在实际使用中，分配给 NVS 的大小一般为多个扇区，NVS 会在多扇区之间分配擦除周期，那么每个扇区的擦除周期的次数必然小于 42k。"
msgstr "According to the `NVS documentation <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/storage/nvs_flash.html>`_, the NVS library mainly uses two entities in its operations: pages and entries. A logical page corresponds to one physical sector of Flash. Assuming the Flash sector size is 4096 bytes, each page can hold 126 entries (each entry is 32 bytes), and the remaining space of the page is used for the page header (32 bytes) and entry state bitmap (32 bytes). The typical Flash lifetime of each sector is 100k erase cycles. Assuming the expected device runtime is 10 years, 4 bytes of data are written to Flash every minute, and Flash encryption is not used: the number of Flash write operations is 60×24×365×10=5256000. In NVS, this will result in no more than 42k erase cycles (5256000/126). Since 42k < 100k, the requirement can be supported even without considering the effect of multiple sectors. In actual use, the size allocated to NVS is usually multiple sectors. NVS distributes erase cycles across multiple sectors, so the number of erase cycles per sector must be less than 42k."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:55 9bb179e3c5944d79ae61fd5b4cb83402
msgid "因此，NVS 可以满足该擦写需求。"
msgstr "Therefore, NVS can meet this read/write requirement."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:60 383f53ca1df44fd5b78411c1e519e7c0
msgid "ESP8266 的模组，有哪些扇区可以自主使用？"
msgstr "Which sectors of ESP8266 modules can be used independently?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:62 1bcc1e2034ca4715b13d2fc0bb15f680
msgid "SDK rel3.0 之前的版本，除 bootloader 与 app bin 外还会在设置的 flash 大小的尾部会保留扇区如下：1 个存放系统信息，1 个存储 ota 信息，1 个存放 RF 校准信息。"
msgstr "For SDK versions earlier than rel3.0, in addition to the bootloader and app bin, the following sectors are reserved at the end of the configured Flash size: one for system information, one for OTA information, and one for RF calibration information."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:63 88c2391f9e374e8fb539728b55669561
msgid "SDK rel3.0 及其以后的版本使用 partition_table 来管理 flash，除改文件自身与 bootloader 外，其余 bin 文件均在 partition_table 标注。"
msgstr "SDK rel3.0 and later versions use partition_table to manage Flash. Except for the partition table itself and the bootloader, all other bin files are marked in partition_table."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:68 391bf30636de4d22b7b3b810ba278c7f
msgid "NVS 是否具有磨损均衡？"
msgstr "Does NVS have wear leveling?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:70 fb5f23eddfd541948a3260da01cadedc
msgid "nvs 使用的不是 esp-idf 中的 wear_levelling 组件，而是在其内部实现的一种擦写平衡机制，使用中 flash 磨损是出于均衡状态。"
msgstr "NVS does not use the wear_levelling component in esp-idf. Instead, it implements an internal erase/write balancing mechanism. During use, Flash wear is kept in a balanced state."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:75 dda185770b8545b2b7f1355e00b03788
msgid "NVS 扇区是否会因写入时意外断电而损坏？"
msgstr "Will an NVS sector be damaged due to unexpected power loss during writing?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:77 565142bb68154195862ff143cbf58cdf
msgid "NVS 设计之初就具有抵抗意外断电的能力，因此不会损坏。"
msgstr "NVS was designed with the ability to withstand unexpected power loss, so it will not be damaged."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:82 4d98cd61dd704696acc9d3054ffaea25
msgid "ESP32 是否可以在外挂的 SPIFLASH 中挂载文件系统分区？"
msgstr "Can ESP32 mount a file system partition in an external SPI Flash?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:84 d8d9d82bdada4a4a8eebb33898f1fd02
msgid "在 esp-idf v4.0 以及之后的版本添加了该功能。需要注意：但是挂载了两个分区时，不能多个任务同时向一个分区写入文件。"
msgstr "This feature was added in esp-idf v4.0 and later versions. Note: when two partitions are mounted, multiple tasks cannot write files to the same partition at the same time."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:89 d4eee9159f874c3da5f4b5e67453ebdb
msgid "意外的断电导致 FATFS 文件系统损坏如何改善？"
msgstr "How can FATFS file system corruption caused by unexpected power loss be improved?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:91 c64bf203ca0c468ab3a38a2dbf3eaa43
msgid "因为 FATFS 设计不支持 write transactions，因此在擦写时意外断电会导致分区错误，并且无法通过简单修改 FATFS 来修复这个问题。目前建议：可以通过创建两个相同的 FATFS 分区进行双备份来从应用层避免该问题，也可以选择使用具有更高安全性的文件系统，如：`LittleFS <https://github.com/joltwallet/esp_littlefs>`_ 和 `SafeFAT <https://www.hcc-embedded.com/safefat>`_ （收费）。"
msgstr "Since FATFS is not designed to support write transactions, unexpected power loss during erase/write operations can cause partition errors, and this issue cannot be fixed by simply modifying FATFS. Current recommendations: create two identical FATFS partitions for dual backup at the application layer to avoid this issue, or choose a more secure file system, such as `LittleFS <https://github.com/joltwallet/esp_littlefs>`_ or `SafeFAT <https://www.hcc-embedded.com/safefat>`_ (paid)."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:96 60853c7790fd4344994e5ccb1fdbe57d
msgid "如何制作并烧录一个 FATFS 文件系统的镜像？"
msgstr "How to create and flash a FATFS file system image?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:98 d18b52213f8e493b98985629379fb0d9
msgid "esp-idf 中未提供相关工具，需要借助第三方工具，完整示例过程如下："
msgstr "esp-idf does not provide a related tool. A third-party tool is required. A complete example process is as follows:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:100 1f6e085e90aa408287813db73636b479
msgid "step1：使用 **`mkfatfs <https://github.com/jkearins/ESP32_mkfatfs>`__** 工具从一个指定文件夹创建镜像，从 file_image 文件夹创建大小为 1048576 Byte ，名为 fat_img.bin 的镜像："
msgstr "step1: Use the **`mkfatfs <https://github.com/jkearins/ESP32_mkfatfs>`__** tool to create an image from a specified folder. Create an image named fat_img.bin with a size of 1048576 bytes from the file_image folder:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:106 fe7a5608e6dd44d08f414104d4fa48ca
msgid "step2：烧录镜像到 0x110000 地址："
msgstr "step2: Flash the image to address 0x110000:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:112 d38f72a6a67147f087101ae2e67003ef
msgid "step3：在程序中挂载："
msgstr "step3: Mount it in the program:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:129 662bd614a9b34a2cbf71cda86d17bde1
msgid "说明：这里烧录的地址一定要是分区表里 fatfs 挂载时对应分区的地址。创建的镜像需要与分区表中设置的大小一致。menuconfig 中的 ``Component config -> Wear Levelling -> Wear Levelling library sector size`` 需要设置为 512，否则挂载失败。"
msgstr "Note: The flashing address here must be the address of the corresponding partition in the partition table when fatfs is mounted. The created image must be the same size as the size set in the partition table. ``Component config -> Wear Levelling -> Wear Levelling library sector size`` in menuconfig must be set to 512; otherwise, mounting will fail."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:134 deda6045de3c43ca84727c7439a0ecbd
msgid "ESP32 是否可以使用 LittleFs 文件系统？"
msgstr "Can ESP32 use the LittleFS file system?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:136 2a45f82e9e4a4fa9bb3afe7dd78348d7
msgid "目前 esp-idf 未包含 LittleFs，存在第三方移植组件 `esp_littlefs <https://github.com/joltwallet/esp_littlefs>`_，可直接在 esp-idf 中使用。匹配 littlefs 文件系统镜像的工具 `mklittlefs <https://github.com/earlephilhower/mklittlefs>`_。"
msgstr "Currently, esp-idf does not include LittleFS. There is a third-party ported component `esp_littlefs <https://github.com/joltwallet/esp_littlefs>`_, which can be used directly in esp-idf. The tool for matching LittleFS file system images is `mklittlefs <https://github.com/earlephilhower/mklittlefs>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:142 c0dbcdae758443939aea0cc5799dc37a
msgid "ESP32 如何查看芯片内存（例如：DRAM、IRAM、rodata）使用情况？"
msgstr "How can ESP32 check chip memory usage, such as DRAM, IRAM, and rodata?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:144 e5df0a7f8b44425080e79fbf922abbad
msgid "可以在工程终端目录下输入 `size-components` 指令来查看相关内存使用情况。"
msgstr "You can enter the `size-components` command in the project terminal directory to check related memory usage."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:145 e1b78493340e4a34a48d046269eb7948
msgid "如 `make size-components` 或 `idf.py size-components`。"
msgstr "For example, `make size-components` or `idf.py size-components`."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:150 f256de3dccfa4b6e950d7dd480456578
msgid "ESP8266 如何读取 Flash 数据？"
msgstr "How can ESP8266 read Flash data?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:152 aa29a847d52a42ba80ba6c04d621ed6e
msgid "可使用 ESP8266-RTOS-SDK 下的脚本工具读 Flash ，读 Flash 方式如下："
msgstr "You can use the script tool in ESP8266-RTOS-SDK to read Flash. The method is as follows:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:154 d79861180a234a48bc7c0cc8c027c17e
msgid "需要安装 python 环境以及工具依赖的包文件"
msgstr "Install the Python environment and the packages required by the tool."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:155 9ec571ba2b604a65814ade4fa63aaec0
msgid "进入 ESP8266_RTOS_SDK/components/esptool_py/esptool 路径下"
msgstr "Go to the ESP8266_RTOS_SDK/components/esptool_py/esptool path."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:156 c7e54ba7c07140618156924592742552
msgid "执行 python esptool.py --chip esp8266 --port /dev/ttyUSB0 --baud 115200 read_flash 0x0 0x400000 esp8266.bin"
msgstr "Run python esptool.py --chip esp8266 --port /dev/ttyUSB0 --baud 115200 read_flash 0x0 0x400000 esp8266.bin"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:157 b5b3e9def9be4d1f9d94f5838b6d684a
msgid "备注：上述命令中 esp8266.bin 为自定义名称，读取到的 Flash 数据将会生成名为 esp8266.bin 的文件，命令中 /dev/ttyUSB0 为 linux 环境中的串口号，其他环境以及系统中会有不同。"
msgstr "Note: In the above command, esp8266.bin is a custom name. The Flash data read will be generated as a file named esp8266.bin. In the command, /dev/ttyUSB0 is the serial port number in a Linux environment; it may differ in other environments and systems."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:162 45dfebd9135547df81b62d301645f3af
msgid "ESP32 模组挂载 8MB PSRAM, 为何实际映射的只有 4MB？"
msgstr "Why is only 4 MB actually mapped when an ESP32 module is mounted with 8 MB PSRAM?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:164 9eea7d149b984a4a8a220e6c80c2ee14
msgid "片外 RAM 最大可映射 4MB(0x3F80_0000-0x3FBF_FFFF) 到数据地址空间,可参考 `ESP32 datahsheet <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_datasheet_cn.pdf>`_ 中的 3.1.4 存储器映射的说明."
msgstr "External RAM can map up to 4 MB (0x3F80_0000-0x3FBF_FFFF) into the data address space. Refer to section 3.1.4 Memory Map in the `ESP32 datasheet <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_datasheet_en.pdf>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:165 83f797ba94f248b8bf28c8e61bf260b2
msgid "可参考例程 `himem <https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/master/examples/system/himem>`_ 访问其余的 4MB 空间."
msgstr "Refer to the `himem <https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/master/examples/system/himem>`_ example to access the remaining 4 MB space."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:168 e0021fe4a68e4911a4c71d79447e1822
msgid "ESP32-CAM开发板和ESP32-Audio-Kit开发板能支持多大的内存卡？"
msgstr "What is the maximum memory card size supported by the ESP32-CAM development board and ESP32-Audio-Kit development board?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:169 535d0a1fd37e44c381b7d1ccea2caa4f
msgid "128G"
msgstr "128G."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:172 547175e07365417582c3cb4419328117
msgid "ESP-12F可以将配置好AT命令保存到FLASH里，开机自动执行进入透传模式吗"
msgstr "Can ESP-12F save configured AT commands to Flash and automatically enter passthrough mode on startup?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:173 34077f246d6e42f0aee5694bd678d401
msgid "部分指令支持保存，具体可以查看AT指令集手册"
msgstr "Some commands support saving. For details, refer to the AT command set manual."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:176 83c2c0d608484c84983be6687cc2492a
msgid "ESP-07S二次开发留给用户的flash和RAM还有多少"
msgstr "How much Flash and RAM are available to users for secondary development on ESP-07S?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:177 cdacee13348f4290abce56e267467d9d
msgid "flash为32Mbit，RAM为80K"
msgstr "Flash is 32 Mbit, and RAM is 80 KB."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:180 73e95af310cd45008a96b65c470815a4
msgid "如何把8266模组里面的所有内容清空"
msgstr "How to erase all contents inside an ESP8266 module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:181 e8e984dadf514b21bc06822f90d87a89
msgid "通过8266烧写上的ERASE按钮进行全部擦除"
msgstr "Use the ERASE button on the ESP8266 flashing tool to perform a full erase."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:184 3e9b54a340864903b3c1faa0318dde04
msgid "ESP-12F能读出已写的固件程序吗"
msgstr "Can ESP-12F read out the written firmware program?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/storage.rst:185 e0ee6c712c6d4d2dac7b3b5b4bd40e48
msgid "可以读取，方法可以查看这个网址https://blog.csdn.net/espressif/article/details/105028809"
msgstr "Yes. For the method, refer to this URL: https://blog.csdn.net/espressif/article/details/105028809"

#~ msgid ":link_to_translation:`en:[English]`"
#~ msgstr ""
